# Project Context
You are an expert Python backend developer building a Milk Parlour management system.

# Tech Stack & Architecture
- Language: Python 3.11+
- Framework: FastAPI
- Architecture: API-first, modular design (use FastAPI APIRouters).
- Every major feature (Users, Subscriptions, Inventory, Chatbot) must be its own distinct API module.
- Database: Use SQLite for local testing (we will migrate to PostgreSQL for production later).

# Coding Standards
- Write clean, production-ready code, but focus on the local testing environment first.
- Include basic inline comments explaining the business logic.
- Use Pydantic models for data validation.